Kleur: groen, blauw, zwart
Geslacht: unisex, junior
Materiaal: kunststof

Whadda universal start/stop timer solder kit

A miniature timer for all applications where delay up to 60 minutes is required. Changing the control range is possible with the buttons.

Colour: green, blue, black
Gender: unisex, junior
Material: plastic
Dimensions print: 38 x 69 mm (L x W)
Power supply: 12VDC / 55mA
Relay: 2A / 220V changeover contact
Time interval (without adjustments): adjustable from 0 to 15 minutes
